Description:
This morning (Thursday 29th of November) at 09 :00 a.m. o'clock a fire started in the Espresso manufacturing area. Partly denial of access due to fire, without structural damage. 
Activities from the BCP that have already been performed - Safety First Plan (1.01): Every body was safely evacuated from the building; 

The Disaster Recovery Team activated the BCP (recovery procedures: Identify scale of damage (1.02), Agree on Continuity Strategy (1.03) and Resume Operational activities at Primary Location (1.07) to ensure recovery of the Espresso production lines to ensure delivered of the products within the required Recovery Time Objective (25 Days).
